## Summary for Quick Reference

| Component | License | Attribution Required |
|-----------|---------|---------------------|
| Modelomics code | MIT | No |
| ESM-C embeddings | Cambrian Open License | Yes - "Built with ESM" |
| E1 embeddings | Profluent-E1 License | Yes - "Built with Profluent-E1" |

**Before using any embedding model, you MUST**:
1. Read the full license at the URLs provided above
2. Understand attribution requirements for your use case
3. Verify you comply with any commercial use restrictions
4. Accept all risks and liability for your use

**Questions about model licenses?** Contact the respective model providers:
- ESM-C: EvolutionaryScale (https://www.evolutionaryscale.ai)
